&lt;p&gt;Work closely with the Art Director and the Art Lead on multiple aspects of character art production, such as Likenesses, hair, rigging and animation balance quality with efficiency when working under tight deadlines, and the hardware constraints of mobile game development. Help with processing and integration of outsourced deliveries. Create&amp;nbsp;and manage the creation of Art builds&lt;/p&gt;
